---
title: Chicken & Mushroom Bibimbap Bowls with Sweet Sesame Sauce & Fried Egg
description: The only thing more fun than saying “bibimbap”? Eating it! Our riff on the classic Korean dish is positively bursting with flavorful veggies. Sweet carrot ribbons, tender zucchini, mighty mushrooms, and pickled scallions are arranged over a bed of steamy rice, just waiting to be mixed up and savored. But not so fast! The bowl gets drizzled with a tantalizing sesame-sriracha-soy sauce, then topped with our favorite accompaniment: a perfect fried egg.
